- {{ill|Takakura Nagayoshi|ja|高倉永祜|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takakura Nagayoshi|qq=|1=Takakura Nagayoshi|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q17226013}}
